<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>The College accepts for exemption and credit scores of 3 or higher on tests taken in approved subject areas in the Advanced Placement (AP) Program.  No credit is given for scores of 1 or 2. A maximum of 30 semester hours may be earned through AP.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.smcsc.edu/Documents/Academics/SMC_Catalog_2010-11.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

